# Track the manifest TS file — it's eagerly imported by icons/providers.ts.
# Generated bytes are tiny (1-2 KB), diff shows up only when icon usage changes (intentional).
# Allowing the CSS files to stay gitignored keeps the high-churn output out of git history.
!main/dashboard/src/styles/auto-gen/icons-subset/manifest.ts
